1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 22=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:37,760
What are you doing?

4
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:55,660
(Xiangmu, Princess Xian'an)

5
00:01:03,470 --> 00:01:05,070
If you're worried,

6
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,430
I can let you keep it.

7
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,000
Look at her,

8
00:01:13,150 --> 00:01:14,870
open-hearted and straightforward,

9
00:01:14,870 --> 00:01:15,710
not like you said.

10
00:01:15,710 --> 00:01:17,263
You're just a crow calling a pig black.

11
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,400
Miss He,

12
00:01:19,710 --> 00:01:21,150
since this pearl is entrusted to you,

13
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,590
I hope you protect it

14
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,200
as carefully as your own life.

15
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:27,920
Miss Bai, don't worry.

16
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,280
I'll try my best to protect it.

17
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:44,200
I wonder how thick the walls are.

18
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,640
How long will it take to dig through?

19
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,000
Do you want some?

20
00:02:02,893 --> 00:02:04,226
Where did the tangerine come from?

21
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,280
I hid it.

22
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,240
Thanks.

23
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,446
There's one more in my pocket.

24
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,240
Here.

25
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,430
I've never missed Huang Long so much.

26
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:21,960
If that jerk were here now,

27
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:23,590
he'd blow it away

28
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:25,000
with two bombs.

29
00:02:25,030 --> 00:02:26,190
If Huang Long were here,

30
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:28,840
you'd probably be dead already.

31
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,000
Nonsense.

32
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,630
If we have a shooting match,

33
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,710
let's see who survives.

34
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:39,710
What's wrong?

35
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,120
A bomb!

36
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,630
Find cover!

37
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:48,470
Run!

38
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,190
Chubby, jump!

39
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:15,400
Huang Long.

40
00:03:17,190 --> 00:03:18,280
We meet again.

41
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,680
Come out.

42
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:21,430
Don't shoot.

43
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:22,280
Hurry.

44
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,750
Hurry up!

45
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:24,750
Come out!

46
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,800
Hurry up!

47
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,590
Let's settle accounts.

48
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:42,680
You stole my box
and took my explosives.

49
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:50,430
What took you so long? Got stuck?

50
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:51,560
Enough talk, move!

51
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,520
Jerk,

52
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:03,430
you pretended to surrender to me.

53
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,630
Is it fun?

54
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:08,590
Even if you killed us all,

55
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:09,910
you'd still fail.

56
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,360
I'll tell you the truth:

57
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,760
That box doesn't contain

58
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:14,680
anything important.

59
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:16,160
What is it then?

60
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:19,360
It's...

61
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:29,750
What is this?

62
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:30,640
Fire!

63
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:32,870
Run! Run!

64
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:57,270
The Bagua layout is correct.

65
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,070
The position is correct.

66
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,440
Chen!

67
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:03,070
Why isn't the main tomb
in the northeast?

68
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:05,070
- It's the fake main hall.
- Chen Youxi.

69
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,310
- Come here.
- Come!

70
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:07,270
What's wrong with you?

71
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,430
- Hurry!
- Come!

72
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,120
The fake main hall should be above.

73
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,920
Why is it below?

74
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,630
What did I do wrong?

75
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:14,710
I...

76
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:27,160
Chen Youxi, what was that?

77
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,320
Chen,

78
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,270
why were you spacing out there?

79
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,273
What were you thinking?

80
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:35,920
Is that giant spider real?

81
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,560
Call me Mr. Li, and I'll tell you.

82
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,630
Mr. Li, my foot.

83
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:42,140
So what if you have a gun?

84
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:43,000
If you have the guts,

85
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,270
go duel that spider alone.

86
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,830
Stop acting mighty with me.

87
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:46,950
I'm sitting here.

88
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:48,390
Come on, shoot over here!

89
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,630
Huang Long, as you can see,

90
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:52,270
if we don't cooperate,

91
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,600
no one gets out.

92
00:05:58,270 --> 00:05:59,870
I'm puzzled.

93
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:01,040
That spider

94
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,950
was driven back before.

95
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,070
Why is it out again?

96
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:08,750
This giant spider must be
the pearl's guardian.

97
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:10,600
We've taken the pearl,

98
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,000
so it won't let us go.

99
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:13,360
It's a beast.

100
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,000
How could it have a guarding instinct?

101
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,720
Maybe it's not guarding,

102
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,040
just pure aggression.

103
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,720
We're not biologists.

104
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,870
For such creatures
beyond our knowledge,

105
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,750
let future experts study them.

106
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,230
Huang Long,

107
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,870
how did you find us?

108
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:29,870
Check your bag.

109
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,560
I put a tracker in it.

110
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,040
When?

111
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:44,040
Don't move.

112
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,830
You were blocked

113
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,040
outside the hidden spring.

114
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,583
How did you get to the fake main hall?

115
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:55,480
The fake main hall?

116
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,750
You mean the four-sided...

117
00:06:57,750 --> 00:07:00,310
I'm asking how you got
to the fake main hall!

118
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,360
The tomb chambers move!

119
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,510
How should I know?

120
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:04,480
Without this tracker,

121
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,070
you'd be long gone.

122
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,390
The chambers move?

123
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,800
If they didn't,

124
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,750
how could I find no doors outside?

125
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,600
The chambers move.

126
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:23,013
The sounds we heard before
weren't illusions;

127
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,750
it's the whole tomb operating.

128
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,950
This is a true living tomb.

129
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,560
You mean

130
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:35,120
it's not just a Bagua array,

131
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,430
it can move?

132
00:07:36,430 --> 00:07:38,270
Exactly.
The magnetic field here is strong.

133
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,240
It's the tomb's spirit.

134
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,750
Could it be

135
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,360
driving the tomb?

136
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:45,950
Then where is the source

137
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,070
of this magnetic field?

138
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:49,310
The Lingxiao Pearl.

139
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:54,216
Do you remember the lotus pedestal

140
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:56,430
holding the pearl?

141
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,480
It kept spinning,

142
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,160
but when we took the pearl,

143
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,830
the moving sound stopped.

144
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,800
Even if everything you said is true,

145
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:06,800
the spinning

146
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,120
must have a pattern, right?

147
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,480
It can't just spin randomly,

148
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,000
or we wouldn't know

149
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,750
where the chamber moved.

150
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,220
(Pearl Cave)

151
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:24,060
(Bronze face)

152
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:25,380
(Soul-locking stair)

153
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:26,620
(Fake main hall)

154
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:28,100
(Sky-Piercing Pavilion)

155
00:08:28,780 --> 00:08:29,660
(Bagua array)

156
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:31,340
(Bell Hall)

157
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:32,940
(Hidden Spring)

158
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,166
(Nether Palace)
I found it.

159
00:08:35,260 --> 00:08:36,840
(Pearl Cave)

160
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,150
I know where the main hall is.

161
00:08:38,415 --> 00:08:39,449
Give me the Wenxiang Jade.

162
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,300
Okay.

163
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,140
(Kan, Dui, Kun, Zhen)

164
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:41,980
(Qian, Xun, Gen, Li)

165
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,440
- Follow me.
- Let's go.

166
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,680
Go.

167
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,560
Right here.

168
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:06,630
All along, the tomb builder

169
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:07,856
kept passing information to us.

170
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,080
The Bagua array told us
the tomb's structure.

171
00:09:10,293 --> 00:09:11,240
The Bell Hall showed us

172
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,400
the tomb's operating pattern.

173
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,120
The main hall entrance is here.

174
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,600
The Lingxiao Pearl.

175
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:10,580
(Xiangmu, Princess Xian'an)

176
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:15,820
(Xiangmu, Princess Xian'an)

177
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:31,670
Right. It's here.

178
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,280
Don't move.

179
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:38,155
Bai Lingling.

180
00:10:38,166 --> 00:10:39,240
- What?
- What do you want?

181
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,080
Step back.

182
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,320
Huang Long,

183
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,080
if you turn on us now,

184
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,270
no one leaves this tomb.

185
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,030
Save that talk for yourself.

186
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,283
Stop wasting time. Let's go.

187
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,960
Do you still think

188
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:01,080
I'm the one who can't leave?

189
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:17,510
Run!

190
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,390
Now, you can tell me.

191
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,440
We have the pearl;

192
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,550
why bring her along?

193
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,510
I have my plan.

194
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,120
But I can guarantee

195
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:41,720
that after this, the pearl is yours

196
00:11:41,822 --> 00:11:42,748
to deliver to the boss.

197
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,240
You won't trick me, right?

198
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,360
Help me this time;

199
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,720
I owe you one.

200
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:51,120
When we're back, the credit is yours.

201
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,200
I won't mind.

202
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:55,550
Bai Lingling, what exactly do you want?

203
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:01,390
Hurry.

204
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,240
We can't beat it?

205
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:19,390
Bai Lingling is such a wench.

206
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,720
We should've listened to Ms. He

207
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,910
and left her behind.

208
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,390
What a Monday-morning quarterback.

209
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:27,480
What's the use of that?

210
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,600
What do you think?

211
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:32,630
If you hadn't been groveling behind her

212
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:34,390
like a lapdog,

213
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:36,440
could Ms. He have been captured?

214
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,030
Who's the lapdog, Lu?

215
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:39,440
Enough, stop bothering me.

216
00:12:58,030 --> 00:13:00,440
This is on me.

217
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,510
If anything happens to her,

218
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,320
I'll pay with my life.

219
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,280
Li Ke,

220
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,720
do you think your life is that valuable?

221
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:22,270
What is Bai Lingling trying to do?

222
00:13:29,150 --> 00:13:31,910
I noticed a detail.

223
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,000
I saw her anxious

224
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:37,200
since entering the cave.

225
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:40,480
Whenever we stop,
she looks at her watch.

226
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:42,320
She seemed rushed before,

227
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:45,600
as if she was in a hurry.

228
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:48,120
What's she in a hurry for?

229
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:52,200
Who knows?

230
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:58,550
Today's the 15th of the lunar month,

231
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,790
nothing special.

232
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:06,360
15th of the lunar month...

233
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:13,390
Let's watch the news to get some news.

234
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,905
(Early morning news)
According

235
00:14:15,916 --> 00:14:17,070
to the Zijinshan Observatory,

236
00:14:17,070 --> 00:14:18,750
at 21:00 on the 28th of this month,

237
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:21,030
there will be
a rare total lunar eclipse.

238
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:23,320
If the weather is good,

239
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,190
people can see

240
00:14:24,190 --> 00:14:26,120
a red moon in the night sky.

241
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:28,750
A red moon?

242
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:30,320
It indicates extreme Yin and cold,

243
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:32,440
showing weak justice,

244
00:14:32,550 --> 00:14:33,870
strong evil,

245
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:35,720
intense resentment,

246
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:39,000
and great malice,

247
00:14:39,270 --> 00:14:41,510
thus called a blood moon.

248
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:43,720
A blood moon.

249
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:48,320
When I got the Lingxiao Pearl,

250
00:14:48,670 --> 00:14:49,903
maybe the strong magnetic field

251
00:14:49,914 --> 00:14:51,240
stimulated my scar,

252
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:53,150
I had a vision flash

253
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,870
of ancient live human sacrifices.

254
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,360
Live human sacrifices?

255
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:58,630
Bai Lingling?

256
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,960
She's from abroad.

257
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:03,000
Why dabble in this superstition?

258
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:08,790
If she wants live sacrifices,

259
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,480
why drag Ms. He along?

260
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,720
Could it be...

261
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:21,710
What time is it?

262
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,800
20:30.

263
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:50,620
(Chen Yao)

264
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:19,396
You do have an ulterior motive.

265
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,600
Thanks to you, I reached here.

266
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:31,120
This is Princess Xian'an's
true main hall?

267
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:34,270
Beautiful, isn't it?

268
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:38,270
Bai Lingling, what do you want?

269
00:16:42,420 --> 00:16:43,260
They're there.

270
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:44,770
What are you doing?

271
00:16:44,790 --> 00:16:45,630
I'll fight her!

272
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,870
With what?

273
00:16:46,870 --> 00:16:48,080
Then what to do?

274
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,630
We have to go down.

275
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:52,414
Lu,

276
00:16:52,425 --> 00:16:53,883
how many pieces of the jade are left?

277
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:54,870
Two.

278
00:16:55,030 --> 00:16:55,870
Give me one.

279
00:16:56,570 --> 00:16:57,410
Wait.

280
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,510
Chen, what are you doing with it?

281
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,320
Using its power.

282
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,160
What?

283
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:24,280
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

284
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:29,640
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

285
00:17:30,700 --> 00:17:35,280
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

286
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:42,430
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

287
00:17:42,990 --> 00:17:54,010
♪La la♪

288
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:02,750
♪No line divides the border♪

289
00:18:03,190 --> 00:18:05,530
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

